$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHuOpNo5.Argh! I can't turn it. It’s stuck.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.…But, I have no idea what it did.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.1Hero, have you recently found another magical item? I can sense some new power.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.Oh, my! Demonic energy, for sure! You need to be very careful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No. I mean, in the air. I was hovering in the air.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx.Well, I’m glad you made it back to the ground. You should be careful with magic you don’t understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The odd thing was, I found it in a chapel on the Wilkes property…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I think Madalyn has something to do with it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoOp.She is up to something, but I don’t know what.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Shit. Melissa is probably mad I’m not in the office again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m out investigating. Do you really want me back in the office?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.I’ve got some more information on your girl, Madalyn.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.What the hell is that supposed to mean?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.The feds sent us their files on Madalyn and there was a DNA match found on the body of Zephaniah.");
